<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012563>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Prothyma (Symplecthyma) coerulea Horn, 1920. a) Dorsal habitus Lectotype, male. b) Dorsal habitus Holotype P. bella Dheurle & Colas, 2018, syn. nov. = P. coerulea opacosericea Horn, 1929 comb. nov.; c) Dorsal habitus Lectotype, male P. coerulea opacosericea Horn, 1929 comb. nov. Scale = 5 mm. d–e Labrum P. coerulea s.str. ST. Scale = 1 mm.: d) Male, e) Female. f–h. Aedeagus. Scale = 1 mm. f) P. coerulea Lectotype. g) Lectotype, male P. coerulea opacosericea Horn, 1929 comb. nov.. h) Holotype P. bella Dheurle & Colas, 2018, syn. nov. = P. coerulea opacosericea Horn, 1929 comb. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012563/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

